{"word":"ἐπισφραγίζω","slug":"ἐπισφραγίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπισφραγίζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> attic <el>ιῶ</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to put a seal on, to confirm, ratify</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to put as a seal upon, impress upon</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>; also as <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be impressed, marked</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}